ias, {name}! Acabas de ganar {commission} de comisión por una nueva venta de referencia (Pedido #{id}). ¡Sigue así!','[{site_name}] Hi {name}, unfortunately one of your referred orders (#{id}) has been {status} and the commission has been removed.'=>'[{site_name}] Hola {name}, desafortunadamente uno de tus pedidos referidos (#{id}) ha sido {status} y la comisión ha sido eliminada.','[{site_name}] Hi {name}, your commission payout of {amount} has been successfully processed! Thank you.'=>'[{site_name}] Hola {name}, el pago de su comisión de {amount} se ha procesado correctamente Muchas gracias.','[{site_name}] Hi {name}, your payout request for {amount} has been received and is being processed.'=>'[{site_name}] Hola {name}, su solicitud de pago de {amount} ha sido recibida y está siendo procesada.','[{site_name}] New affiliate registration from {name} ({email}) is awaiting your approval.'=>'[{site_name}] Nuevo registro de afiliado de {name} ({email}) está esperando su aprobación.','[{site_name}] New referral sale! Affiliate {name} (coupon: {coupon}) earned {commission} commission on order #{id}.'=>'[{site_name}] ¡Nueva venta por recomendación! El afiliado {name} (cupón: {coupon}) ha ganado {commission} por el pedido #{id}.','[{site_name}] Order #{id} by affiliate {name} has been {status}. Commission removed.'=>'[El pedido #{id} del afiliado {name} ha sido {status}. Comisión eliminada.','[{site_name}] Payout of {amount} sent to affiliate {name} (payout #{id}).'=>'[{site_name}] Pago de {importe} enviado al afiliado {nombre} (pago #{id}).','A custom "manual" payment method of your choice.'=>'Un método de pago "manual" personalizado de tu elección.','A direct bank transfer payment method (paid manually).'=>'Un método de pago por transferencia bancaria directa (pago manual).','a discount'=>'un descuento','A fixed amount earned for sub-affiliate referrals'=>'Una cantidad fija ganada por referidos de subafiliados','A login form will be displayed on the affiliate dashboard f